</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA040290-0044 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 198461 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 2, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 5; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
