UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; ENGLAND -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- 
IRAQ; STING OPERATIONS; UNITED STATES -- ARMS SALES -- MIDDLE EAST 
</P>
