<TEXT>
<P>
Nelson R. Mandela said today he will meet President Frederik W. de Klerk on 
Thursday to discuss ways to end the factional violence among blacks in Natal 
province, and he appealed for an end to the fighting that has kept blacks from 
uniting to fight white minority rule. 
</P>
